{"tid":486602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爬頭擋賓利　貨Van司機囚4周","createTime":"2017-12-02T04:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T05:04:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"685225ce359a7720f9ad6427d6f5bab5f6cd04ea","tid":486602,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232219&d=GAyoW2IVBjKVGnhFwJyaoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7daa85f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232219&h=c86eb19b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232219</a><br />\n<br />\n爬頭擋賓利　貨Van司機囚4周<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】火爆司機在清水灣道駕駛客貨車落斜，嫌前方賓利跑車駛得慢，盛怒下連環報復，多次爬頭切線在賓利前急停，又把客貨車打橫攔住兩條行車線阻賓利去路。閘車狂漢早前承認一項危險駕駛罪，昨求情指當時被惹起情緒，令他「好似發咗癲咁」，他亦有感「大家都咁衰」而報警，期望與跑車事主「一齊停牌」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171202/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171202%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=c66ab952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告曾石良用客貨車閘停賓利後（左圖），以多部手機拍攝司機及乘客（右圖）。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n停牌兩年　須讀改進課程<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批評被告駕駛態度惡劣，案情嚴重須判監，判監4星期、停牌2年。被告曾石良（36歲）早前於承認今年9月2日犯案。兩年的停牌令在出獄後才開始生效，他並須修讀駕駛改進課程。<br />\n<br />\n案發時賓利前座女乘客用手機拍下的片段後來在互聯網流傳，引發網民一面倒唾罵被告。庭上昨播放案發片段，跑車司機報警時要求警方盡速到場，「唔該盡快，因為條友過嚟敲我個窗，好似癲咗」，女乘客則語帶驚慌。被告有多項刑事案底及逾10項交通前科，現涉其他案件候審。辯方承認被告態度令人厭惡，但肇事後沒有不顧而去。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC2003/17<br />\n■記者羅日昇、伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"5fe3d345a6f52af8972adb53b081e37515181ddf","tid":486602,"uid":20325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"81c58dc63262c687c29703f857ecc3a787e2d943","tid":486602,"uid":135957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f5f884fd2b4df3a597ef2958fa2f1a4817004b6","tid":486602,"uid":57962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae79159cd235a5a447b65873f422fa5753ab403b","tid":486602,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有多項刑事案底及逾10項交通前科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簡直當條路係佢 推鳩人咪算囉"},{"pid":"d5802df6d0cb54ff4624d0802428b83e2b744f35","tid":486602,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"癡線個車主玩死你都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a910a8597f491738a6b2ed66ffb51345cc85698","tid":486602,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"咁多前科得坐4個星期？<br />\n你估佢未停完會唔會照揸車周街飛"},{"pid":"af513a1775253d6290384fb070205ef01d4cdbe4","tid":486602,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多前科得坐4個星期？<br />\n你估佢未停完會唔會照揸車周街飛</blockquote><br />\n停兩年牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd49b8da29ec6d1dc25ef15dd1bdc28326f73a98","tid":486602,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"抵啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19536dcaf9b1c707dd3323954abdd597f4c8a6ea","tid":486602,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"咁少？屌你老母睇片完全係危險駕駛"},{"pid":"dc266f89a11a10fd097b3c34b779e2946278a5ae","tid":486602,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike"